                                </div>
                                <div class="content">
                                    <p><strong>Feb 18 at 9 AM - 2 PM</strong></p>
                                    <p><strong>Blocks 1-6</strong></p>
                                    <p>HOA Office - <a href="tel:0321234567">(032) 123-4567</a></p>
                                    <p>Scheduled power maintenance. Change devices in advance.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="ann-Card birthday">
                                <div class="header">
                                    <i class="bi bi-balloon-fill icon" style="background-color: #ff69b4;"></i>
                                    <span>Birthday Celebration</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="content">
                                    <p><strong>Feb 18 at 12 PM - 4 PM</strong></p>
